descriptionHTML:
Eye watch face is an analogue watch face with beautiful graphics and display style. The needles are graphically designed hands pointing towards the accurate time. Also it displays battery status and current date.
Eye watch face is carefully designed with ambient mode as well as standard mode functionality.
